{"tid":1113774,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高柏尼：哥帥令曼城變「贏波機器」","createTime":"2019-04-18T06:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T06:47:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"948c0d295e0d34a708f2bde4d0e95440356e6e94","tid":1113774,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"曼城隊長高柏尼表示，藍月亮力足成為本季「歐洲四冠王」，因為領隊哥迪奧拿功力深厚，成功將球隊變為一部「贏波機器」，球隊的力量絕非來自個人，而是來自球會的整體力量。<br />\n<br />\n今季雖然有奇雲迪布尼「傷多過踢」，左閘班捷文文迪亦長期養傷，不過曼城成績依然一流，早前已奪得英聯盃冠軍，現時亦打入英足盃決賽，英超方面是失分最少球隊，歐聯亦殺入8強。<br />\n<br />\n高柏尼表示：「就算球隊陣容不整，但哥迪奧拿都可以找到其他球員去盡展自己所長，來為球隊作出貢獻。我們的優秀表現，並非維持一場半場，又或者一個月兩個月，而是長期的發揮出高水準。過去18個月中，你根本不可以從球隊中找出一個特別突出的球員，因為我們踢的整體足球。哥帥將曼城變為贏波機器，實在難以勒住我們。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=4665df7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"7e35e1046a30a168c5cc69952d12596c75964474","tid":1113774,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:14:36.000Z","msg":"Ederson: 我係一個壞咗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/b969078efad9366d0e6fd6dfca1bc32c/tumblr_pq4j9yRraA1w50dq4o1_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fb969078efad9366d0e6fd6dfca1bc32c%2Ftumblr_pq4j9yRraA1w50dq4o1_540.gif&h=e94f0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/08320e496a2459894bea3abfc38c8416/tumblr_pq4j9yRraA1w50dq4o3_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F08320e496a2459894bea3abfc38c8416%2Ftumblr_pq4j9yRraA1w50dq4o3_540.gif&h=d9b4905d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63364c625a36379f2215bfb964e73b0bfc317327","tid":1113774,"uid":3194,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"鏝同鈀一撚樣, 國內聯賽就威威, 出去歐聯就柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\